name: Series one design 1
description: Stain clothing is a U.K. based urban clothing company that has been created to bring a fresh new range of street wear for people of all ages and all sizes. We sell every colour and style of men’s t-shirts that you could imagine and our sizes range from the tiny SMALL to the mighty XXL. All of our fresh designs come straight from the black book of the U.K. graffiti artist stain himself and he strives to get both originality and quality within all of his pieces. You are buying an awesome Graffiti T-shirt from the new Brand Stain Clothing. This label will be huge, so be sure to get a piece of this brand before everyone else does . . .
